WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:06.300
I know you have something to ask

2
00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:07.666
It can be said now

3
00:00:08.600 --> 00:00:10.700
You marry Song Yawei

4
00:00:10.700 --> 00:00:13.200
Is it because he looks like his sister?

5
00:00:13.700 --> 00:00:14.566
No.

6
00:00:15.700 --> 00:00:17.200
And for what?

7
00:00:17.933 --> 00:00:19.466
You don't need to know why.

8
00:00:19.666 --> 00:00:21.333
I just want to ask you one question now

9
00:00:21.333 --> 00:00:22.800
Are you really going to marry Xu Ze?

10
00:00:25.066 --> 00:00:27.366
This is the same as you and Song Yawei

11
00:00:27.366 --> 00:00:28.866
Does it matter?

12
00:00:29.500 --> 00:00:30.833
As long as you don't marry Xu Ze

13
00:00:31.300 --> 00:00:32.433
I can get married again

14
00:00:33.400 --> 00:00:34.700
Pardon me?

15
00:00:34.900 --> 00:00:37.466
Chuan, we should go to the hotel

16
00:00:38.866 --> 00:00:40.233
I'm waiting for your answer.

